<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV120">
<l>iyakkaṟāta palpiṟappi leṉṉaimāṟṟi yiṉṟuvan</l>
<l>tuyakkoḷmēka vaṇṇaṉaṇṇi yeṉṉilāya taṉṉuḷē</l>
<l>mayakkiṉāṉṟaṉ maṉṉucōti yātalāleṉ ṉāvitā</l>
<l>ṉiyakkelāma ṟuttaṟāta viṉpavīṭu peṟṟatē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The liberating cloud-hued [Lord] [wished to] remove me from the many births</l>
<l rend="indent">That do not leave,</l>
<l>Came today and approached [me], mixed His permanent light in Him[self]</l>
<l rend="indent">existing in me.</l>
<l>Therefore, my soul severed all motions and obtained liberation that is bliss</l>
<l rend="indent">which remains unsevered.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
